sequenceDiagram
    participant OS as Operating System
    participant CM as ConfigManager
    participant SP as StoragePool
    participant BT as SystemBootstrapper
    participant NL as NetworkLayer

    OS->>CM: Load("kbms.ini")
    CM-->>OS: Biến cấu hình (Host, Port, DataDir)
    OS->>SP: Initialize(DataDir, MasterKey)
    SP-->>OS: Catalog Ready
    OS->>BT: Bootstrap()
    BT->>BT: Verify/Create System KB
    BT-->>OS: System Ready
    OS->>NL: Start(TcpListener)
    NL-->>OS: Listening on Port...
